---
title: Rump Steak & Twice-Cooked Herby Potatoes Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Tender rump steak is seared to perfection and is topped with a home-made garlic and parsley
compound butter. We think the real star of the show is the twice-cooked roast potatoes - don’t worry, we’ve given you all the tips to achieve your crispiest roasties yet!

